留意有否非法改裝<br />\n<br />\n「叻媽教室」指出，不少人在居屋裝修時都會改裝廚廁，主因可解決「開門見廁」的風水問題，以及改成開放式廚房增加空間感，然而廚廁對調等工程有機會涉及5大問題︰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T23:57:45.000Z","msg":"非法改裝無關買家事，去小額追佢，死都唔還就玩到佢釘契"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"簽臨約正約<br />\n兩份都白紙黑字寫明成交唔到就殺訂賠傭<br />\n自己疏忽冇留意到有大改動，怪得邊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"佢層樓唔適合賣，呢個已經夠，個交易本身就不可能發生，因為業主犯法。唔使考慮咁多，做佢得架啦。"},{"pid":"38362e36cd6f9e79cdb86119336f76e5e000b5d1","tid":2513690,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6014fd045c4b260a2b0df7a52e2b7151bc939796","tid":2513690,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"81c81f92e36c457ce863b401c82ff16fe38dd131","tid":2513690,"uid":359522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f2efd3ee9c123c15ec5b63d04174f4a40ad822fb","tid":2513690,"uid":136735,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T23:11:23.000Z","msg":"改開放式廚房 入則係基本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T23:22:25.000Z","msg":"想入則申請都難，基本上大部份單位廚房係正單位入囗附近，要加裝消防花灑頭同煙霧感應器，點變成套消防系統出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T23:28:19.000Z","msg":"住家講咩野消防花灑丫？<br />\n你住公廠定公家位？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:55:23.000Z","msg":"訓撚醒未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咩鳩野呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撚樣"},{"pid":"966a7555def1a5f40b0da753cae4f1cabcac0c0f","tid":2513690,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38362e36cd6f9e79cdb86119336f76e5e000b5d1","tid":2513690,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6014fd045c4b260a2b0df7a52e2b7151bc939796","tid":2513690,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"81c81f92e36c457ce863b401c82ff16fe3